{"tid":1594856,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"一具浮屍，竟然令意大利獨裁者墨索里尼倒台！！！！！！！！！","createTime":"2019-09-25T18:30:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T08:26:29.000Z","uid":22675,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e7868a292a729477c4dbf391862fea9962046468","tid":1594856,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T18:30:48.000Z","msg":"二戰期間，Glyndwr Michael 本是一名英國威爾斯流浪漢，但不幸誤食老鼠藥身亡。因 Glyndwr 無親無故，所以英國情報機關在盟軍入侵西西里前，决定徵用其屍體進行擾敵任務，代號 Operation Mincemeat。<br />\n<br />\nGlyndwr Michael 被穿上英國皇家海軍制服，打扮成高級軍官 William Martin。他身上除了証件，更重要是藏有偽造機密文件，顯示盟軍將會進攻希臘及意大利撤丁島，以擾亂軸心國視線。<br />\n<br />\n準備妥當後，Glyndwr Michael 由潛艇送到西班牙海岸。當地人發現一件黃色物體載浮載沉，於是報警。<br />\n<br />\n西班牙法西斯警察到場，認為有可疑，於是隨即驗証。當發現那份僞造文件，覺得事態嚴重。雖然西班牙在二戰屬中立國，但仍與納粹眉來眼去，所以情報仍然被送到德國情報部門手上。<br />\n<br />\n德國收到假情報後，信以為真，立即調動軍隊，增兵希臘及撒丁島，間接讓路給盟軍入侵西西里。<br />\n<br />\n一具浮屍，竟然間接令意大利獨裁者墨索里尼倒台，步向敗亡。<br />\n<br />\n圖為 1943年4月，Glyndwr Michael 遺體穿上英國皇家海軍制服，頸上掛上黄色救生衣，準備出發。<br />\n<br />\nPhoto from Cassowary Colorizations<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cassowarycolorizations/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcassowarycolorizations%2F&d=nuTNs4p9zVAmxGYrSBNXTtC8ckn1nBU%2Fwr2%2FVciPwp8%3D&h=6a16bd9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cassowarycolorizations/</a>"},{"pid":"f6cbda86aef5fe8e967520f41fe8ce50e785dd85","tid":1594856,"uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T18:33:11.000Z","msg":"沒有 fact check 的後果"},{"pid":"68350275170ca2d7bb48bb7a982a840a34daffe5","tid":1594856,"uid":22675,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T18:33:34.000Z","msg":"這告訴我們假新聞的殺傷力"},{"pid":"7867ba00786326cab64b58d14703df9ea058a3b8","tid":1594856,"uid":319687,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T18:51:16.000Z","msg":"咁成日放D屍出黎既目的又係咩呢?<br />\n佢大可以收埋什至燒佐佢,<br />\n點解又要揾克警放係海度或者整D自整自殺案出黎呢?<br />\n<br />\n唔通係<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呀爺陰克警?</span></span></strong><br />\n唔會既, 呀爺最<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">鍚</span></span></strong>就係克警"},{"pid":"7a89ab4c12172f8a1361f70285471a737b9a5f0d","tid":1594856,"uid":15644,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T18:53:22.000Z","msg":"其實咁多條屍<br />\n大陸求其運d 落黎dum 落海容乜易<br />\n如果黑警真係殺左人 一定毀屍滅跡<br />\n洗乜拋落海比你影到大頭"},{"pid":"c8b91c24b0315869a0cc702f1df304a4a10bf4ff","tid":1594856,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T05:56:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5939de351daf08de51f8ea64ecf99d3e66c2606","tid":1594856,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T08:24:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"505c92d1425831f6b3c9ef57f0fe580d625f08b9","tid":1594856,"uid":53034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T08:26:29.000Z","msg":"push"}]}